{"name":"AI 语音录入","dsl":{"schema":"2.0","config":{"update_multi":true,"style":{"text_size":{"normal_v2":{"default":"normal","pc":"normal","mobile":"heading"}}}},"body":{"direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"12px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px","elements":[{"tag":"img","img_key":"IMG_KEY_TODO","preview":true,"transparent":false,"scale_type":"fit_horizontal","corner_radius":"8px","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":":GoGoGo:  **问卷开口即填，降低录入负担｜数据表一贴即成，告别手动搬运**","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"column_set","flex_mode":"stretch","horizontal_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","elements":[{"tag":"interactive_container","width":"fill","height":"auto","corner_radius":"8px","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"<font color='blue'>**问卷支持 AI 语音录入** \n</font>","text_align":"center","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**• 打乱语序也能对**：连续说、跳着说或整段叙述，AI 自动识别意图并归位填入","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**• 口语表达也能懂**：支持语义理解，将非标准口语智能映射为精准的表单选项","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**• 复杂环境也能填**：为一线场景考虑，车间、工地等喧闹场景也能精准捕捉信息","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}],"has_border":false,"background_style":"blue-50","padding":"12px 8px 12px 8px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}],"vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","weight":1},{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","elements":[{"tag":"interactive_container","width":"fill","height":"auto","corner_radius":"8px","elements":[{"tag":"markdown","content":"<font color='blue'>**数据表支持 AI 粘贴录入** \n</font>","text_align":"center","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**• 轻轻一粘 AI 录入**：在空白处轻轻 Ctrl + V ，AI 自动识别图片/文本并生成数据表\n","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**• 看得懂复杂图片**：大模型直接\"看\"图，像人眼一样理解表格结构，精准还原\n\n\n\n","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"markdown","content":"**• 搞得定各种场景**：智能识别网页、PDF、PPT 等任意截图，提升数据整理效率","text_align":"left","text_size":"normal_v2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}],"has_border":false,"background_style":"blue-50","padding":"12px 8px 12px 8px","direction":"vertical","horizontal_spacing":"8px","vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}],"vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","weight":1}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"hr","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"column_set","horizontal_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","columns":[{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","elements":[{"tag":"button","text":{"tag":"plain_text","content":"了解 AI 语音录入"},"type":"primary","width":"fill","size":"medium","behaviors":[{"type":"open_url","default_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/827223408763-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%A3%9E%E4%B9%A6%E9%97%AE%E5%8D%B7#tabs0|lineguid-ixrzu","pc_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/827223408763-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%A3%9E%E4%B9%A6%E9%97%AE%E5%8D%B7#tabs0|lineguid-ixrzu","ios_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/827223408763-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%A3%9E%E4%B9%A6%E9%97%AE%E5%8D%B7#tabs0|lineguid-ixrzu","android_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/827223408763-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%A3%9E%E4%B9%A6%E9%97%AE%E5%8D%B7#tabs0|lineguid-ixrzu"}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}],"vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","weight":1},{"tag":"column","width":"weighted","elements":[{"tag":"button","text":{"tag":"plain_text","content":"了解 AI 粘贴录入"},"type":"primary","width":"fill","size":"medium","behaviors":[{"type":"open_url","default_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/333406176860-%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E5%A4%9A%E7%BB%B4%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95#tabs0|lineguid-rBjOO","pc_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/333406176860-%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E5%A4%9A%E7%BB%B4%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95#tabs0|lineguid-rBjOO","ios_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/333406176860-%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E5%A4%9A%E7%BB%B4%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95#tabs0|lineguid-rBjOO","android_url":"https://www.feishu.cn/hc/zh-CN/articles/333406176860-%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E5%A4%9A%E7%BB%B4%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95#tabs0|lineguid-rBjOO"}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}],"vertical_spacing":"8px","horizontal_align":"left","vertical_align":"top","weight":1}],"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},{"tag":"div","text":{"tag":"plain_text","content":"功能已经正式上线，期待你的反馈和建议。","text_size":"notation","text_align":"left","text_color":"grey"},"icon":{"tag":"standard_icon","token":"person-admit_outlined","color":"grey"},"margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px"}]},"header":{"title":{"tag":"plain_text","content":"🧨 多维表格新春 AI 能力上新：AI 语音录入 & AI 粘贴录入"},"subtitle":{"tag":"plain_text","content":""},"text_tag_list":[{"tag":"text_tag","text":{"tag":"plain_text","content":"功能上新"},"color":"green"}],"template":"blue","padding":"12px 12px 12px 12px"}},"variables":[]}